From 4b36dfa55291ecd19de85cd1de4be1bdd58376fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GW2 WvW Log System <gw2-log-system@example.com>
Date: Sat, 9 May 2026 01:58:42 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix: add all missing build module files ignored by .gitignore

The frontend/.gitignore 'build/' pattern incorrectly ignored all
directories named 'build' anywhere in the tree, including source
directories under src/. This commit adds all missing files:

- src/api/build/build.ts, skills.ts
- src/models/build/build.ts, skills.ts
- src/services/build/bdCodeService.ts, buildsService.ts, skillRotationService.ts
- src/store/build/buildLibrary.ts
- src/views/build/BuildLibraryView.vue, BuildParserView.vue, BuildSkillRotationView.vue

Also changes .gitignore to '/build/' to only ignore root-level build output.
